== Joyce uwamahoro ==
'''Joyce uwamahoro''' ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwandakazi]] ndetse akaba yikorera ibijyanye n'imideli akaba ariwe washinze '''joyce fashion designs''' iherereye i [[Kigali]] mu isoko rya Nyarugenge<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/business/entrepreneurs-experience-how-start-fashion-house-2020</ref> .

yashinze joyce fashion designs muri 2018.


== Umwuga ==
