bituma atangira kugenda abona abikiriya batandukanye hirya no hino bimwe mu bikorwa bye harimo; Guma mu Rugo Collection,Nyampinga dedicated Collection, ingenzi 

collection. akaba akora iyi mideli yabagabo ndetse nabagore afite  intego yo kugirango u Rwanda rwihaze mu bijyanye ni isoko ry'imyenda ndetse bibashe no kugera ku rwego mpuzamahanga<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/joyce-fashion-designs-yashyize-hanze-imyambaro-yageneye-abashaka-kurimba</ref> .

